Interface Summary
ChartProvider Provides a chart type and series to create a ChartView.

OutputDatasetProvider Provider of a simulation output dataset for a given run number.
Saveable A Saveable object.

REXPDatasetProvider Provides a pre-existing REXP as a dataset.

ROutput1DMultiRun An output dataset produced by running commands on the scape dataframe in R.
SaveableDataset A Saveable CDataCacheContainer.
StatsRowsChartProvider A ChartProvider derived from a StatsRows object.
